Ngaphambi kokuba lezi zingane zibulawe, uPhasha wayebhala kwiFacebook esola unkosikazi wakhe ngokumjolela, wathi wamthelela ngegciwane ingculazi. Wabe esesho ukuthi izingane zakhe uKatlego (9), Joyce (7) Tshepo (5) no- Adel (3) ngeke aphinde azibone. “Ungidinile kabi nje lona (esho unkosikazi), nabangani bakhe nathandana nabo. Ngeke esasibona futhi kumele abulawe yigciwane lengculazi. Unkosikazi wami ungizwise ubuhlungu,” kubhala uPhasha kwiFacebook. Waphinde wafaka nesithombe sikankosikazi wakhe emgagula ukuthi unegciwane, ethi uhamba elala. Icala lizobuyela maduze enkantolo. Umsolwa usagcinwe esitokisini.